<view class="page pt-6 {{fontScaleClass}}">
  <view class="container">
    <view class="header card mb-24">
      <text class="eyebrow">工友守护·薪工记</text>
      <text class="title-lg mt-8">今天工时记了吗？</text>
      <text class="subtitle mt-8">每天记一笔，月底核对工资、扣款和到账金额更清楚。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="dashboard-card card mb-24">
      <view class="flex-between">
        <view>
          <text class="section-label">{{dashboard.todayLogged ? '今日已记' : '今日待记'}}</text>
          <text class="dashboard-title mt-8">{{dashboard.hint}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="dashboard-state {{dashboard.todayLogged ? 'done' : 'todo'}}">
          {{dashboard.todayLogged ? '✓' : '记'}}
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="dashboard-grid mt-20">
        <view class="dashboard-metric">
          <text class="metric-value">{{dashboard.monthDays}}</text>
          <text class="metric-label">本月记工天数</text>
        </view>
        <view class="dashboard-metric">
          <text class="metric-value">{{dashboard.monthHours}}</text>
          <text class="metric-label">本月工时(h)</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view
      class="primary-entry card mb-24"
      data-path="{{primaryAction.path}}"
      data-tab="{{primaryAction.isTab}}"
      bindtap="onTapEntry"
      hover-class="card-hover"
      hover-stay-time="100"
    >
      <view class="primary-copy">
        <text class="section-label">建议先做</text>
        <text class="primary-title mt-8">{{primaryAction.title}}</text>
        <text class="primary-sub mt-8">{{primaryAction.subtitle}}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="primary-mark">记</view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="section-title">常用自查</text>
      <text class="section-desc">合同、金额和材料先做核对，重要结果会保存在记录里</text>
    </view>

    <view class="tool-list mb-24">
      <view
        class="tool-card card"
        wx:for="{{tools}}"
        wx:key="key"
        data-path="{{item.path}}"
        data-tab="{{item.isTab}}"
        bindtap="onTapEntry"
        hover-class="card-hover"
        hover-stay-time="100"
      >
        <view class="tool-tag">{{item.tag}}</view>
        <view class="tool-copy">
          <text class="feature-title">{{item.title}}</text>
          <text class="feature-sub mt-6">{{item.subtitle}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="section-title">记录中心</text>
      <text class="section-desc">合同自查和金额测算结果会集中保存在这里</text>
    </view>

    <view class="quick-grid mb-24">
      <view
        class="quick-item card"
        wx:for="{{quickLinks}}"
        wx:key="key"
        data-path="{{item.path}}"
        data-tab="{{item.isTab}}"
        bindtap="onTapEntry"
        hover-class="card-hover"
        hover-stay-time="100"
      >
        <text class="quick-title">{{item.title}}</text>
        <text class="quick-sub mt-6">{{item.subtitle}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="boundary-card card">
      <text class="boundary-title">服务边界</text>
      <text class="boundary-text mt-8">本工具用于记录、测算和常见规则自查，内容仅供核对参考，不替代专业机构意见，也不代办任何处理事项。</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
